    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >驾驶行星漫游车，穿越迷失在沙地中的废墟，探寻隐藏在沙丘深处的秘密。将战利品卖给当地人，完成他们的任务，了解这些地方疯狂的过去。为您的交通工具配备先进设备，从最隐蔽的角落开采更多宝石和稀有动物皮，到达遥远的山丘。但要注意时间：可怕的生物可能会在夜幕的掩护下来拜访你，你可别高兴得太早......</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225650/extras/a132e116d97c6f26719f8939889ebaf0.poster.avif?t=1770275855\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225650/extras/a132e116d97c6f26719f8939889ebaf0.webm?t=1770275855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225650/extras/a132e116d97c6f26719f8939889ebaf0.mp4?t=1770275855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索沙丘，揭开秘密</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在新阿卡姆殖民地重新开始您的生活 从这里开始，您将进入沙漠，在古老建筑的废墟中搜寻宝藏，捕捉巨型生物和巨型剑齿虫（共有 30 多种）。探索洛夫克拉夫特发明的每个区域，完成任务并前往邻近的奇幻区域，每个区域都有自己独特的特征、居民和秘密。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225650/extras/0cc169c7177c083c213dcc92f1d57c0b.poster.avif?t=1770275855\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225650/extras/0cc169c7177c083c213dcc92f1d57c0b.webm?t=1770275855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225650/extras/0cc169c7177c083c213dcc92f1d57c0b.mp4?t=1770275855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挖掘文物</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有人很想让你挖掘过去，但他们可信吗？疯狂是会传染的。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225650/extras/7f5cbc50f68f1980268d1eb43649e637.poster.avif?t=1770275855\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225650/extras/7f5cbc50f68f1980268d1eb43649e637.webm?t=1770275855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225650/extras/7f5cbc50f68f1980268d1eb43649e637.mp4?t=1770275855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夜间小心</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >危险无处不在：小心巨大的虫子和躲藏的鹅。但最糟糕的是，太阳一落山，沙地就会被黑暗笼罩....。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225650/extras/b1e6a91ff13dcb1ea04dd5c159ae7f71.poster.avif?t=1770275855\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225650/extras/b1e6a91ff13dcb1ea04dd5c159ae7f71.webm?t=1770275855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225650/extras/b1e6a91ff13dcb1ea04dd5c159ae7f71.mp4?t=1770275855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏特色</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >揭开终极之谜：驾驶行星漫游车，您可以前往荒野中失落的栖息地，每个栖息地都有自己的居民，如 Mi-Go、Tindal、Yog-Sothoth、Nyarlathotep、Elder Ones 和 others....。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >挖矿：宝藏就在泥沙和碎石中等待着你，完成当地人的任务将帮助你获得许多独特的技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >磨练你的手艺：学习新装备，升级你的全地形车，猎杀稀有怪物，寻找埋藏的宝藏和神秘文物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >狩猎谋生：通过向当地人出售猎物，您可以了解地球上发生的事情，改进您的漫游车，前往更偏远的地方。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >反击疯狂：强化你的头脑，利用你学到的知识在日落后可怕的沙漠中生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225650/extras/903b500ae95b683fd8dd43f0bf01597b.poster.avif?t=1770275855\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225650/extras/903b500ae95b683fd8dd43f0bf01597b.webm?t=1770275855\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3225650/extras/903b500ae95b683fd8dd43f0bf01597b.mp4?t=1770275855\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
